{
  "texts": [
    "Besides tokenization, POS-Tagging is an option for the NER preprocessing step.",
    "Familiar entities, such as PER, LOC, and ORG, are nouns.",
    "POS-tagging can speed up and simplify recognizing entities based on nouns.POS-Tagging conceptually has a similar task to NER: annotating the text.",
    "POS-Tagging performs text annotations based on part-of-speech such as nouns, pronouns, verbs, adverbs, prepositions, and others.",
    "Meanwhile, NER performs annotations based on certain entities such as a person, location, and organization."
  ]
}